learnings[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-25T17:55:23.972Z",codex-agent,Large dogfood audits benefit from exercising command contracts programmatically (help JSON + contracts) to catch registry-wide regressions early while keeping deterministic exit-code checks.
  "2026-04-25T20:04:34.346Z",codex-agent,"When wrapping Commander actions, mutate processed args through command._processArguments and option value sources instead of patching listener argument shapes directly."
